data.description: Adorable brick ranch nestled in an established neighborhood near the Naval Hospital, shipyard, restaurants, and shopping. Renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and an open concept dining and living area. Beautiful hardwood floors have been refinished and newer windows. Three bedrooms, including a huge primary bedroom with plenty of storage space with 3 closets.  Remodeled bathroom with a tiled shower.  Don't miss out on this beautiful property with an beautiful front porch! Fence installed in 2022.
